{
  "design_notes": "The chart is built for dance pads on Medium difficulty. The intro establishes a solid baseline with quarter-note steps and periodic holds to represent the sustained notes. In S1 (the first main drop), the texture shifts to a stream with rhythmic eighth-note steps to capture the high energy. The movement changes to a zigzag pattern to keep the player moving naturally. S2 winds down slightly but keeps a light drift to guide the player toward the break. During the quiet S3/S4 break and outro, we place sparse steps on key beats to ensure there are no long dead pauses while giving the player a comfortable breather.",
